# ClassStoreGraph
Create class store graph from your class store


[![](https://mermaid.)](https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid-live-editor/#)

```mermaid
classDiagram
	class ClassStoreDot {
	}
	class ClassStoreMermaid {
	}
	class ClassStoreGraph {
	}
	class EntitySelection {
	}
	class Entity {
	}
	class DataClass {
	}
	class _DataStore {
	}
ClassStoreGraph <|-- ClassStoreDot
ClassStoreGraph <|-- ClassStoreMermaid
Object <|-- ClassStoreGraph
Object <|-- EntitySelection
Object <|-- Entity
Object <|-- DataClass
Object <|-- _DataStore
```
